      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must have documented version control, regression testing, and configuration management consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) has documented release notes and internal validation suite, but project-level configuration management records are incomplete. No formal regression test suite was executed for the hemolysis-specific user-defined functions. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
