      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code must be verified against analytical solutions or benchmark problems for the relevant flow physics at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against lid-driven cavity and pipe flow benchmarks. Hemolysis power-law UDF was not independently verified against an analytical solution. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
