      "rationale": "Solver residuals reported (continuity < 1e-5, momentum < 1e-5) but no formal analysis of iterative convergence error contribution to hemolysis QoI. Round-off error not assessed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
