      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Potential for analyst error in model setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing must be assessed and mitigated at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "No independent model review or peer verification of boundary condition specification performed. UDF implementation for hemolysis not independently checked. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
