      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used in validation must be characterized for variability and representativeness at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood samples from a single supplier used across all experiments. Inter-sample variability in hematocrit and viscosity not systematically characterized. Number of biological replicates insufficient for statistical characterization at MRL 5. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
