      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis performed between validation and COU input parameter sets. Blood rheology parameters differ between bovine (validation) and human (COU) blood. Inlet velocity profiles from validation test rig not characterized and assumed equivalent to COU. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
